{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Operations Guide{% endblock %}

{% block pageContent %}
<div class="min-h-[80vh] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="relative isolate overflow-hidden rounded-3xl bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-emerald-900/30 to-cyan-800/20 p-10 shadow-xl mb-10">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-30" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="absolute -left-10 -top-10 h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-cyan-500 blur-3xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 h-72 w-72 rounded-full bg-indigo-500 blur-3xl"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="relative space-y-4 max-w-4xl">
            <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-cyan-200/80 flex items-center gap-2">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" class="size-5 opacity-80">
                    <path d="M3 12h18"></path>
                    <path d="M8 7l-2 5 2 5"></path>
                    <path d="M16 7l2 5-2 5"></path>
                    <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle>
                </svg>
                Operational Checklist
            </p>
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white leading-tight">From campaign setup to yearly balance.</h1>
            <p class="text-lg text-slate-200/90">Segui questi step per mettere online una campagna Traveller con navi, equipaggi, costi/entrate e mutui, fino all’Annual Budget.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-200/70">
                <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Campaign first</span>
                <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Shipyard & Crew</span>
                <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Costs & Income</span>
                <span class="badge badge-outline badge-sm">Mortgage & Budget</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 1</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Crea la Campaign</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Definisci titolo, descrizione e session calendar (giorno/anno). Tutte le date future (mutui, pdf, form) ereditano da qui.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 2</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Crea le Ship</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Registra le navi. Possono essere PC o NPC: per le NPC puoi saltare mutuo, costi e income se non servono.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 3</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Crea le Companies</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Aggiungi controparti con ruoli e signLabel. Servono per mutui, costi e income.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 4</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Collega le Ship alla Campaign</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Associa ogni nave a una Campaign: così le date usano il calendario di sessione centralizzato.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 5</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Crea Crew e collegali</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Inserisci gli equipaggi, assegna i ruoli e collega le persone alle navi corrette.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 6</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Registra i Cost</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Inserisci i costi per nave e categoria, con dettaglio delle linee di spesa (detail items) e pagamento.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 7</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Registra gli Income</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Aggiungi entrate per nave e categoria (Freight, Contract, ecc.) con dettagli dedicati e PDF stampabili.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 8</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Crea i Mutui</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Per le navi con finanziamento: imposta tasso, assicurazione, rate; firma con data di sessione e location; stampa il PDF (anche draft).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-base-200/80 p-6 shadow-sm">
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-cyan-400 mb-2">Step 9</p>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-100">Crea l’Annual Budget</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-slate-300 mt-2">Per ogni nave: aggancia ricavi, costi e rate pagate nell’anno corrente e visualizza il bilancio e il grafico temporale.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{% endblock %}
